room_title: Escape room "Saint Angelo's Castle" by Komnata Quest in San Antonio
review: We had the best date night at Komnata Quest! We chose the castle, which was a great immersion into the dark life in that time period. We will be going back!

room_title: Escape room "Saint Angelo's Castle" by Komnata Quest in San Antonio
review: Some friends and I just did Saint Angelo's Castle and it was AWESOME! The theming was incredible. It was super intense and so much fun! Yulia was wonderful and sweet and helpful! Thanks for a great time!
